            <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d1909.6099379818768!2d96.17016563994106!3d16.815444777948123!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x30c1ecb43025ef7f%3A0x82981f6f6cc08d2a!2sS+Race+Course+St%2C+Yangon%2C+Republic+of+the+Union+of+Myanmar!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1424680962006"> </iframe>
